comments.message:
Seems like you're adding it by default.
I would think it might be best to install it only if 'GRAPHITE_HOST' is set for instance.

You're getting a -2 because your commit message is not correct.

You need to have an empty line after the first line.

Also Resolves: and Change-Id: should be in the same block.
This is also valid for the other change.
